tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query:
SELECT useraction.name as "Actions", COUNT(*) as "Number of Actions", count(distinct usersession.internalUserId) as "Users", median(duration) as "Duration", sum(useraction.requestErrorCount) as "Errors" 
FROM useraction 
WHERE usersession.osFamily="Android" 
GROUP BY useraction.name 
ORDER BY COUNT(*) DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query:
SELECT device as "Device", count(*) as "Sessions", sum(useraction.requestErrorCount) as "Errors", sum(numberOfRageTaps) as "Rage Clicks" 
FROM usersession 
WHERE usersession.osFamily="Android" and hasCrash=false 
GROUP BY device 
ORDER BY count(*) DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query:
SELECT device as "Device", count(*) as "Sessions", sum(useraction.requestErrorCount) as "Errors", sum(numberOfRageTaps) as "Rage Clicks" 
FROM usersession 
WHERE usersession.osFamily="Android" and hasCrash=true 
GROUP BY device 
ORDER BY count(*) DESC

tiles.name: User Sessions Query
tiles.query:
SELECT appVersion, hasCrash, count(*) as "Sessions", MEDIAN(userActionCount) as "Median user action count", sum(useraction.requestErrorCount) as "Errors", sum(numberOfRageTaps) as "Rage clicks" 
FROM usersession 
WHERE usersession.osFamily="Android" 
GROUP BY hasCrash, appVersion 
ORDER BY appVersion DESC, hasCrash
